OL,3,CCovid bereaved families accuse
OL,4,CStormont leaders of 'ignoring' them
OL,6,FMembers of the Covid Bereaved Families
OL,7,Ffor Justice NI group have criticised
OL,8,FFirst Minister Michelle O'Neill and
OL,9,Fdeputy First Minister Emma Little
OL,10,FPengelly for failing to meet with them
OL,11,Fprior to formulating and publishing
OL,12,Fthe Executive's formal response to the
OL,13,Ffirst phase of the UK-wide inquiry
OL,14,Finto the pandemic.
