OL,3,CCovid bereaved families accuse
OL,4,CStormont leaders of 'ignoring' them
OL,6,FThey revealed that four letters
OL,7,Frequesting a meeting ` sent in July,
OL,8,FSeptember, October and November last
OL,9,Fyear ` went without a substantive
OL,10,Fresponse before January's publication
OL,11,Fof the Executive's response to the
OL,12,Finquiry's Module One recommendations.
OL,14,FThe Module One recommendations dealt
OL,15,Fwith improving civil contingencies
OL,16,Farrangements to make sure authorities
OL,17,Facross the UK are better prepared for
OL,18,Fa similar health emergency in the
OL,19,Ffuture.
