OL,3,CCovid bereaved families accuse
OL,4,CStormont leaders of 'ignoring' them
OL,6,FThe group finally received a reply
OL,7,Ffrom the Executive Office on Tuesday
OL,8,Fafternoon accepting the request for a
OL,9,Fmeeting ` a response that came just
OL,10,Fhours before a planned press
OL,11,Fconference by the families on
OL,12,FWednesday morning to highlight the
OL,13,FExecutive's approach to them.
OL,15,FA meeting is now due to take place at
OL,16,FStormont on Monday.
OL,18,FMartina Ferguson, whose mother Ursula
OL,19,Fdied in the pandemic, questioned the
OL,20,Ftiming of the response.
