OL,3,CCovid bereaved families accuse
OL,4,CStormont leaders of 'ignoring' them
OL,6,F"We feel we've been ignored," she said.
OL,8,F"I mean, we've made those requests as
OL,9,Fsoon as the inquiry had made their
OL,10,Frecommendations, and we would have
OL,11,Fexpected to be involved before now.
OL,13,F"That's seven months. I mean, a lot of
OL,14,Fwork from a group of people with lived
OL,15,Fexperience could have helped the
OL,16,FExecutive in the last several months."
OL,18,FShe added: "It was just another
OL,19,Ffailure ` we were dismissed."
