OL,3,CCovid bereaved families accuse
OL,4,CStormont leaders of 'ignoring' them
OL,6,FMs Ferguson said the group was "very,
OL,7,Fvery surprised" by the timing of the
OL,8,Fmeeting invite, just before the group
OL,9,Fwas due to go public with its
OL,10,Fcriticism of the Executive's response.
OL,12,FBut she said the group welcomed the
OL,13,Ffact that a meeting would now
OL,14,Feventually take place.
OL,16,FBrenda Doherty, whose mother Ruth died
OL,17,Fin the pandemic, said Monday's meeting
OL,18,Fmust not be a "token" gesture.
OL,20,F"I see Monday as a start," she said.
