OL,3,CCovid bereaved families accuse
OL,4,CStormont leaders of 'ignoring' them
OL,6,F"The proof will be in the pudding as
OL,7,Fto how we move forward. This is not
OL,8,Fgoing to be a token gesture. We are
OL,9,Fnot here for the sake of it."
OL,11,FSolicitor Enda McGarrity from PA Duffy
OL,12,F& Co Solicitors, which represents the
OL,13,Fbereaved families' group, noted that
OL,14,Fthere would be nine further module
OL,15,Fresponses developed by the Executive
OL,16,Fas the inquiry progresses.
OL,18,FHe expressed hope Stormont's leaders
OL,19,Fwould adopt a different approach with
OL,20,Fthe families going forward.
