OL,3,CCovid bereaved families accuse
OL,4,CStormont leaders of 'ignoring' them
OL,6,F"At this point, there's still time to
OL,7,Fturn things around," he said.
OL,9,F"There needs to be a U-turn in how the
OL,10,FExecutive involves these families in
OL,11,Fthe process.
OL,13,F"Their experience gives them an
OL,14,Finsight that others do not have, and
OL,15,Fthe sooner that's recognised, the
OL,16,Fsooner we can get on with the work of
OL,17,Fimplementing the recommendations that
OL,18,Fkeep everyone safe."
OL,20,FThe Executive Office has been
OL,21,Fapproached for comment.
